                                <td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=599&amp;sid=4bd51089cec5de5ba6f4b085b8467db0#599"><img src="templates/RPGGvPS2/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Tue Oct 01, 2002 10:17 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Transporting from a ritual circle</span></td>
                                <td valign="top" align="right" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=599&amp;sid=4bd51089cec5de5ba6f4b085b8467db0"><img src="templates/RPGGvPS2/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
