                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It is impossible to Transport whilst a Ritual is in progress (ie. the Seal to Edreja / The Barrier is in place).
<br />

<br />
When the seal is removed (and the seal to the void restored) it is possible to transport. At this stage, a Ritualist may transport out up to 15 people, or if more are present within the circle, 15 people, apparently at random! This can include any undesirables within the circle at the time !
<br />

<br />
If the Ritual is specifically to prepare for a transport, as opposed to any other effect, more than 15 people could be transported at this point.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
