                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">At one of the bard's Gorsedds, it was three days away from a roitual circle and some Sylvan elves came. Somebody asked them how come we hadn't seen them walking behind us since they were only a few hours behind us, and I'm fairly sure they said they'd done a ritual to transport straight to the area we were in to avoid walking.
<br />

<br />
It was a while ago though and I only heard it in passing and had other things on my mind that weekend, so I might be wrong.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
