                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have seen Skavern using Warpstone to transport 20 people using a standard circle. Of course they did burn out the destination circle in the process, and the Skavern doing it died.
<br />

<br />
I have also seen synchronous transport - where 3 groups are sent simultaneously from seperate circles to arrive at a destination circle together. None of the circles involved seemed to suffer any ill effects from this.
<br />

<br />
I have never directly seen a ritual used to transport on Edreja, but the theory of such things would certainly allow it. It seems somewhat wasteful of power - and decidedly risky - to do it that way though.<br />_________________<br />Dain Stormcrow
<br />
Captain at Arms, The Militia</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
