                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It is quite possible for several groups to arrive in a circle together. Frequently, though, they are seperated in time. A transport does not take a fixed period, so though one may try to coordinate several arrivals at once, they may not arrive at once in practice.
<br />

<br />
This technique was used by the first two groups, at least, in the assault on The Isle of Dreams at the Heartland Games.
<br />

<br />
Master Earth</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
